WEBVTT

00:03:59.840 --> 00:04:01.816
I was 34 years old,

00:04:01.840 --> 00:04:05.496
and I had calculated that American banks

00:04:05.520 --> 00:04:08.376
had lent much more money
to emerging countries

00:04:08.400 --> 00:04:11.216
than those countries
were going to be able to pay back

00:04:11.240 --> 00:04:13.936
and that we would have
the greatest debt crisis

00:04:13.960 --> 00:04:15.320
since the Great Depression.

00:04:16.200 --> 00:04:18.416
And with it, an economic crisis

00:04:18.440 --> 00:04:20.480
and a big bear market in stocks.

00:04:21.680 --> 00:04:23.680
It was a controversial view at the time.

00:04:24.160 --> 00:04:26.600
People thought it was
kind of a crazy point of view.

00:04:27.480 --> 00:04:29.696
But in August 1982,

00:04:29.720 --> 00:04:31.680
Mexico defaulted on its debt,